#: fpcupdeluxemainform.upconsent
msgid ""
"Attention !\n"
"\n"
"Fpcupdeluxe is able to log some install info.\n"
"(Country, OS, Versions, Up-Actions)\n"
"This data is send towards a mORMot server,\n"
"where it is made available to anybody.\n"
"(see URL shown in screen and statusbar)\n"
"\n"
"Do you allow this logging info to be gathered ?"
msgstr ""
"注意！\n"
"\n"
"Fpcupdeluxe 可記錄部分安裝資訊。\n"
"(國家、作業系統、版本、更新動作)\n"
"這些資料會傳送至 mORMot 伺服器，\n"
"並對所有人公開。\n"
"(請參閱畫面及狀態列中顯示的網址)\n"
"\n"
"是否允許收集這些記錄資訊？"

#: fpcupdeluxemainform.updarwinfolderwarning1
msgid "FPCUPdeluxe cannot be run inside the Downloads folder."
msgstr "FPCUPdeluxe 無法在「下載項目」資料夾中執行。"

#: fpcupdeluxemainform.updarwinfolderwarning2
msgid "This is NOT allowed by OSX security measures."
msgstr "macOS 安全性機制不允許此操作。"

#: fpcupdeluxemainform.updarwinfolderwarning3
msgid "Copy FPCUPdeluxe into its own directory and run from there."
msgstr "請將 FPCUPdeluxe 複製到獨立的目錄中再執行。"

#: fpcupdeluxemainform.upfolderwarning1
msgid "FPCUPdeluxe could not create its necessary setting-files."
msgstr "FPCUPdeluxe 無法建立必要的設定檔。"

#: fpcupdeluxemainform.upfolderwarning2
msgid "Please check the folder permissions, and re-start."
msgstr "請檢查資料夾權限，然後重新啟動。"

